{"type":"message","id":"20682439","parentId":"a77e921d","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:18:04.844Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01FouHfNK6eaJyQArT539pPj","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Memory Log — 2026-03-06\n\n## QMD Setup\n- Installed QMD v1.0.7 as memory backend for openclaw\n- Configured Claude Code MCP integration via ~/.claude/settings.json\n- Two collections: `workspace` (system .md files) and `memory` (daily logs)\n- openclaw memory.backend set to \"qmd\" with searchMode \"query\" (hybrid BM25+vector+reranking)\n- Embeddings running on CPU (Intel Mac, Metal fallback pending)\n\n## User Preferences\n- Prefers concise responses without emojis\n- Working directory: ~/.openclaw\n- Telegram channel enabled, WhatsApp not configured\n\n## Test Entry\n- The pink elephant dances at midnight near the golden fountain.\n# Session: 2026-03-07 00:02:48 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:telegram:direct:1771281565\n- **Session ID**: e7b1a1ac-af79-4935-9d20-4a0fde3c2e0c\n- **Source**: telegram\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"58\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1771281565\",\n  \"sender\": \"N TT\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-06 19:02 EST\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"N TT (1771281565)\",\n  \"id\": \"1771281565\",\n  \"name\": \"N TT\",\n  \"username\": \"ntthein\"\n}\n```\n\nHi\nassistant: [[reply_to_current]] Hey! 👋 What's up?\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"60\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1771281565\",\n  \"sender\": \"N TT\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-06 19:02 EST\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"N TT (1771281565)\",\n  \"id\": \"1771281565\",\n  \"name\": \"N TT\",\n  \"username\": \"ntthein\"\n}\n```\n\nTell me about it past chat\nassistant: [[reply_to_current]] Let me pull up the recent session history.\nassistant: Looks like this is actually a **brand new conversation** — there's no prior chat history between us beyond what just happened:\n\n1. You said **\"Hi\"**\n2. I replied **\"Hey! 👋 What's up?\"**\n3. You asked about past chats\n\nThat's the full history. This appears to be our first exchange! Were you expecting previous conversations, or is there something specific you'd like to talk about? 😊"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"# Memory Log — 2026-03-06\n\n## QMD Setup\n- Installed QMD v1.0.7 as memory backend for openclaw\n- Configured Claude Code MCP integration via ~/.claude/settings.json\n- Two collections: `workspace` (system .md files) and `memory` (daily logs)\n- openclaw memory.backend set to \"qmd\" with searchMode \"query\" (hybrid BM25+vector+reranking)\n- Embeddings running on CPU (Intel Mac, Metal fallback pending)\n\n## User Preferences\n- Prefers concise responses without emojis\n- Working directory: ~/.openclaw\n- Telegram channel enabled, WhatsApp not configured\n\n## Test Entry\n- The pink elephant dances at midnight near the golden fountain.\n# Session: 2026-03-07 00:02:48 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:telegram:direct:1771281565\n- **Session ID**: e7b1a1ac-af79-4935-9d20-4a0fde3c2e0c\n- **Source**: telegram\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"58\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1771281565\",\n  \"sender\": \"N TT\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-06 19:02 EST\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"N TT (1771281565)\",\n  \"id\": \"1771281565\",\n  \"name\": \"N TT\",\n  \"username\": \"ntthein\"\n}\n```\n\nHi\nassistant: [[reply_to_current]] Hey! 👋 What's up?\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"60\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1771281565\",\n  \"sender\": \"N TT\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-06 19:02 EST\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"N TT (177